          <ul>
            <li><p>Roles:<em>Healer,Ranged Spell-Casting Damage Dealer</em></p></li>
            <li>Available to:<img src="img/heroes/Priest/02.png" alt="Priest 1" />
            </li>
            <li><img src="img/heroes/Priest/03.png" alt="Priest 2" /></li>
            <li><p>Specializations:<em>Discipline<img src="img/heroes/Priest/Spell01.png" alt="Spec 1" />,Holy   <img src="img/heroes/Priest/Spell02.png" alt="Spec 2" />,Shadow <img src="img/heroes/Priest/Spell03.png" alt="Spec 3" /></em></p></li>
          </ul>
