            <li><p>Specializations:<em>Balance<img src="img/heroes/Druid/Spell01.png" alt="Spec 1" />,Feral <img src="img/heroes/Druid/Spell02.png" alt="Spec 2" />,Guardian <img src="img/heroes/Druid/Spell03.png" alt="Spec 3" />,Restoration <img src="img/heroes/Druid/Spell04.png" alt="Spec 4" /> </em></p></li>
