            </li>
            <li><img src="img/heroes/Hunter/03.png" alt="Hunter 2" /></li>
            <li><p>Specializations:<em>Beast Mastery<img src="img/heroes/Hunter/Spell01.png" alt="Spec 1" />,Marksmanship <img src="img/heroes/Hunter/Spell02.png" alt="Spec 2" />,Survival <img src="img/heroes/Hunter/Spell03.png" alt="Spec 3" /></em></p></li>
